high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink
Pick up an egg from the counter.
Turn around and go to the microwave
Heat the egg in the microwave then take the egg out
Turn to the right and go to bread on the counter
Put the egg by the bread on the counter
anns.task_desc: Cook an egg in the microwave

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the kitchen sink
Pick up the egg from behind the tomato
Turn around and walk to the microwave above the counter
Put the egg in the microwave, cook it, and remove it
Move a few feet left and face back toward the counter with bread on it
Put the egg on the counter left of the bread loaf
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked egg on the kitchen counter

high_descs: Turn right to cross the room, hang a right at the silver fridge to reach the sink.
Pick up the white egg behind the tomato on the sink.
Turn around, cross the room and hang a right at white dishwasher to face the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the egg on the far right side of the blue plate, heat it for three seconds, remove the hot egg from the microwave, and close the door.
Turn right until you reach the counter and then turn left to face the shelf above the counter top.
Place the egg to the left of the loaf of bread on the shelf above the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated egg on a shelf.
